		{"id":"dc2d42e0f50954dd","type":"text","text":"**Common AI Perception Component**\n\n- Set linked **AI Controller** by code (allow the comp to be elsewhere than on the AI Pawn/Controller) and the **AI Perception Component**.\n- Set vars for perception rules (range, etc)\n- Register to the **AI Perception Subsystem**.","x":0,"y":-480,"width":610,"height":300,"color":"6"},
