		{"id":"bc9d81070d4b1a90","type":"text","text":"**Other Actor that can trigger the sense**\n\nThis contains a **AI Perception Stimuli Source Component**\n","x":-990,"y":-130,"width":560,"height":220,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"24018ea607019a80","type":"text","text":"**Global Perception System**\n\nThe AI senses you if:\n- it **see**s you\n- it **see**s an object marked as \"linked\" to the player. For example an object pushed by the player, or spawned.\n- If other AIs that meets the above criteria's are close enough (since real humans would \"tell\" others what they saw), this also has an option for testing for in-between collisions\n\nYou then use the senses events to drive your AI behaviours.","x":-520,"y":-840,"width":620,"height":320,"color":"1"}
